@startuml
title US14 - Domain Model Excerpt

hide methods
hide circle
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

' Conceitos do Negócio baseados no DM original [cite: 2]
abstract class StaffMember {
  - name : String
  - postalAddress : String
  - phone : String
  - email : String
  - citizenCardNumber : String
}

class Receptionist extends StaffMember
class Nurse extends StaffMember
class DGSAdministrator extends StaffMember

' Notas de Regras de Negócio (Business Rules)
note right of StaffMember
  **AC14-1:** Each employee has a single role (Subclass).
  **AC14-2:** Name, Phone, Email are mandatory.
  **AC14-3:** Phone and CC Number must be valid PT format.
  **AC14-4:** Phone and Email must be unique in the system.
end note

@enduml